/nav>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Spirits of the Deceased</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\"><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">亡</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>ぼう</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">霊</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>れい</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby></span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Bōrei</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Installing Japanese character sets\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#198975;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is the seventh chapter of <a href=\"/wiki/Koyoharu_Got%C5%8Dge\" title=\"Koyoharu Gotōge\">Koyoharu Gotōge's</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" title=\"Kimetsu no Yaiba (Manga)\">Kimetsu no Yaiba</a>.\n<p></p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Summary\">Summary</span></h2>\n<p>The chapter starts off with <a href=\"/wiki/Makomo\" title=\"Makomo\">Makomo</a> asking <a href=\"/wiki/Sabito\" title=\"Sabito\">Sabito</a> if their intuition to believe in Tanjiro was correct to which he responds, \"I don't know but no amount of effort is too much.\"\n</p><p>Back at the Selection, Tanjiro is beginning to face the <a href=\"/wiki/Hand_Demon\" title=\"Hand Demon\">Hand Demon</a> who informs him of his reign as one of the strongest demons on the mountain, he also reveals that it was <a href=\"/wiki/Sakonji_Urokodaki\" title=\"Sakonji Urokodaki\">Urokodai</a> who trapped him on the mountain to begin with. As the children daunt on the stunning claims, the demon begins to taunt Tanjiro by saying that he has eaten many of Urokodaki's students before and that he would be next.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/1/1a/The_Hand_Demon%27s_delight.png/revision/latest?cb=20180611233700\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/The_Hand_Demon's_delight.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"150\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:The_Hand_Demon%27s_delight.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">The Hand Demon mocking Tanjiro</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>In a shocking turn of events, the demon reveals that he has claimed the lives of 13 of Urokodaki's students with two specific ones being the most memorable. The demon describes the strongest student as having peach colored hair and a scar by his mouth, as well as the most agile student as a girl who wore a floral kimono.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tright show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/c/c9/The_Hand_Demon%27s_blow.png/revision/latest?cb=20180611225247\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/The_Hand_Demon's_blow.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"167\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:The_Hand_Demon%27s_blow.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Tanjiro gets knocked out</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>After having realized that the demon was describing both Sabito and Makomo, Tanjiro lashes out and attacks the demon after he makes insulting remarks regarding Makomo's death. Sabito remarks that Tanjiro's emotions are starting to interfere with his focus and he ends up getting momentarily knocked out after being slammed into a tree.\n</p><p>The child initially hunted by the demon decides to escape while Tanjiro is attacked, abandoning him for dead. Tanjiro remains knocked out and is about to be killed by the demon when <a href=\"/wiki/Shigeru_Kamado\" title=\"Shigeru Kamado\">Shigeru appears</a> in his dreams begging him to wake up to which he immediately responds by slicing the demons arm off. Tanjiro continues to evade the demons attacks and persists forth until the demon's life thread finally becomes visible before Tanjiro's eyes.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Makomo\" title=\"Makomo\">Makomo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sabito\" title=\"Sabito\">Sabito</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hand_Demon\" title=\"Hand Demon\">Hand Demon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sakonji_Urokodaki\" title=\"Sakonji Urokodaki\">Sakonji Urokodaki</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Shigeru_Kamado\" title=\"Shigeru Kamado\">Shigeru Kamado</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\